Distribution and ecology. Santa Marta , Colombia . It inhabits rocky shores and coral reefs, 3–36 m in depth, usually only on overhanging substrata at shallow depths ( 3–8 m ), and more exposed and abundant in the deeper reef ( 14–36 m ), where it may cover up to 5.4 % of the hard substrata (cf.
Zea 1993
).
